{"tid":1285434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日既事完全唔會令我想自殺, 反而令我既生存意志更加堅定","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T18:07:31.000Z","uid":66260,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d2b32d5edc7395b2377216f4a656e6b8811540","tid":1285434,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"<em>「他那些仇人本來都已四五十歲，再隔上這麼四十多年，到那時豈還有不一個個都死了？哈哈，哈哈，其實他壓根兒不用費心想甚麼破法，鑽研甚麼武功，只須跟這些仇人比賽長命。四十多年比下來，老天爺自會代他把仇人都收拾了」- 射鵰英雄傳</em><br />\n<br />\n年青人們，如果你地絕望既來源係呢因為班豬狗不如既高官, 咁你更加唔可以輕生<br />\n你一死, 你就再冇機會睇住佢地後尾嗰幾年點折墮, 你早過佢地死, 你就輸左俾佢<br />\n<br />\n我諗野好單調亦好天真, 對住呢班仆街既然冇任何方法可以懲罰佢地, 咁唯有用大自然最基本既自然定律收佢地皮<br />\n呢班畜生大你四五十年, 自然會早你四五十年死 (如遇上皇天擊殺等意外, 即時死亡則更好), 只要你留住有用之軀, 到時笑到最後既就係你<br />\n<br />\n約定心灰意冷既大家, 當689, 777出殯之日, 我地一齊去佢靈堂播小鳳姐好唔好?<br />\n喺呢一日來臨之前, 我地都唔可以做傻事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e708ab7477d8b3b063569a5e00c0c8481a665d6c","tid":1285434,"uid":162272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"仲有班00後新移民"},{"pid":"7e92d79c5576c48c84cfe362fd755dff861e13b3","tid":1285434,"uid":66260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e708ab7477d8b3b063569a5e00c0c8481a665d6c","tid":1285434,"uid":162272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"仲有班00後新移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"00後新移民都好, 肯為香港付出既就係真香港人"},{"pid":"870188a40704442a22bbc34f6b1c8648e655f16c","tid":1285434,"uid":46674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"推 唔好再有下一個"},{"pid":"a9140295ad8ef8f06d315b249623fe55d72c4228","tid":1285434,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bd2842c7c837e001b589b9ba2fecbbf7907b5a","tid":1285434,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262f0302f934466ed68edfddba2abc7ab51a2305","tid":1285434,"uid":68668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"請理解身邊的人 適當地給予援手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"304d430e2e7ddf0c3704b13e533e2d30f6f38fcc","tid":1285434,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"想輕生嘅同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285464</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今次真係見到香港人其實好撚有愛好撚團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好離開我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b37663aa8ab13d138b3ff81c9440080b1e7289","tid":1285434,"uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"6月開始<br />\n我覺得香港好有愛<br />\n真香港人好嘅本性出番黎<br />\n把聲大過鄰國人<br />\n有啲變番去舊香港以前咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋喺00 後身上<br />\n我睇到香港有希望<br />\n希望大家要橕住<br />\n<br />\n我認我分化<br />\n真香港人就是不一樣"},{"pid":"5a28d1eadbd2736baa6ea077d957cc7883f992cd","tid":1285434,"uid":49918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b6a202699558eb85fb63ea3733c83331f52d951","tid":1285434,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a28d1eadbd2736baa6ea077d957cc7883f992cd","tid":1285434,"uid":49918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:08:4